Task1

spark_df = spark.read \
          .csv("sample.csv")

 
sount_df = spark_df \
        .where("Age < 40") \ 
        .select("Age", "Gender", "Country") \
        .groupBy("Country") \
        .count()

This is an Action

sount_df.show()

Now to validate this move this code to def function.

def count_by_country(survey_df: DataFrame) -> DataFrame:  
    return survey_df \  
        .where("Age < 40") \  
        .select("Age", "Gender", "Country", "State") \  
        .groupBy("Country") \  
        .count()
